Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.34,0:00:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新机动战记-钢弹W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.54,0:00:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.01,0:00:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.55,0:00:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.66,0:00:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱着你被淋湿的肩膀 想温暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.87,0:00:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,颤抖的指尖 彷徨地在找什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.67,0:00:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的视线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.95,0:01:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲伤变为力量的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.39,0:01:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.06,0:01:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.70,0:01:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.40,0:01:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.28,0:01:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔?怎么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.28,0:01:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望你告诉大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.78,0:01:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要在我面前出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.25,0:01:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否则
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.99,0:01:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会杀死大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.56,0:01:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我说过不要接近我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.26,0:01:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想说的只有这些话吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.71,0:01:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果一切都疯狂的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.24,0:01:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就会相信自己而战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.91,0:02:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔，我要杀死你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.62,0:02:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十五话\N[卡特尔对希洛]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.19,0:03:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,防护罩也到了极限吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.46,0:03:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.46,0:03:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们为何在战斗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.40,0:03:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星和OZ联手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.40,0:03:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星变成敌人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.41,0:03:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对特洛瓦和希洛你们来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.44,0:03:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星也是敌人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.98,0:03:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙疯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.25,0:03:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我要把一切毁灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.95,0:03:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对吧?希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.67,0:04:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你会死啊，希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.87,0:04:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我不想打倒同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.80,0:04:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我求你，快逃，希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.84,0:04:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你听到吗?希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.08,0:04:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.98,0:04:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.85,0:04:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的背后有卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.44,0:04:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.44,0:04:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已经很讨厌那个卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.41,0:04:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和钢弹交战中的宇宙里欧部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.18,0:04:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,及特洛瓦‧巴顿驾驶的拜叶特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.75,0:04:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有回音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.55,0:04:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,推测和麦丘留士一起全军覆没了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.52,0:04:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.66,0:05:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星毁灭了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.53,0:05:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还没，卫星没有很大的损毁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.80,0:05:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，战斗还在继续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.07,0:05:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了保护卫星而战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.57,0:05:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是真正钢弹驾驶员的模样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.44,0:05:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能阻止新钢弹的行动就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.98,0:05:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,里欧的母舰有影像进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.18,0:05:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，把这些资料送去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.75,0:05:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月面基地的钢弹技师手上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.95,0:05:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该能得到些情报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.22,0:05:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.62,0:05:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校，现在联络不到月面基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.99,0:05:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.83,0:05:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兹巴洛夫技师长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.00,0:05:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴尔吉要求打开通讯线路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.40,0:05:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有联络进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.67,0:05:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.40,0:05:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪尔麦优侯爵的指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.17,0:05:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是叫我加快生产MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.68,0:05:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉里看来有不稳的动静
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.15,0:05:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本不能信任人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.52,0:05:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD成为\N新战士的时代来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.89,0:06:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老人家果然镇定啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.06,0:06:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,空气即将用完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.86,0:06:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,意识快要失去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.53,0:06:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们还末消灭OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.43,0:06:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到就这样子死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.03,0:06:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想看一眼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.10,0:06:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重新出现的钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.87,0:06:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死神和神龙的改良还未完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.31,0:06:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.45,0:06:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.99,0:06:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到…真的就此死去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.47,0:06:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五飞…好威风啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.90,0:06:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的[地狱死神]…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.34,0:06:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有了它…OZ根本不堪一击啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.74,0:06:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你做什么…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.51,0:07:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死了吗…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.71,0:07:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五飞…我好寂寞…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.35,0:07:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陪我直到最后啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.19,0:07:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这家伙…在停止呼吸吗…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.03,0:07:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他说这叫龟息…吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.10,0:07:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这家伙真厉害…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.23,0:07:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,未到最后不放弃希望…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.17,0:07:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对啊…我不能就此死去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.68,0:07:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.95,0:07:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以输…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.46,0:07:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,离开机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.99,0:07:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对你那样说也没用呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.23,0:07:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，我要打倒你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.96,0:07:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要动手的就快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.00,0:07:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没打算和敌人啰唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.20,0:07:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再见，希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.05,0:08:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.92,0:08:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为你错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.49,0:08:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.36,0:08:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这场战斗是没必要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.47,0:08:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦!快离开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.94,0:08:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜叶特要爆炸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.67,0:08:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.44,0:08:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我到此为止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.31,0:08:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.48,0:08:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛!停手!特洛瓦他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.93,0:08:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.97,0:09:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.47,0:09:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以什么形式也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.94,0:09:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星和OZ联手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.31,0:09:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样表示一场战争已经完结
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.01,0:09:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同时，我们的任务也完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.98,0:09:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对为了卫星而战的我们来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.89,0:09:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星改变了主意是遗憾的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.36,0:09:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但这是战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.52,0:09:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们只有接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.96,0:09:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之后是被遗弃的士兵的问题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.23,0:09:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是我们心里的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.80,0:09:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,未成熟的我们身为士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.74,0:09:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直过于倚靠完美的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.94,0:09:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由于一直认真战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.31,0:09:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以即使只有自己一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.98,0:09:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们也认为能改变这时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.01,0:09:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔，那不只你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.98,0:09:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都是那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.08,0:09:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，那种心把仁慈的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.92,0:09:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,推进痛苦的死胡同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.86,0:09:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我们心里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.66,0:10:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们自己要战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.56,0:10:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且一定要残酷地找出结论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.60,0:10:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使一直以来的战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.63,0:10:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,变成无意义也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.47,0:10:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来不得不承认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.90,0:10:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们是…这时代\N不再需要的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.18,0:10:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，卡特尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.71,0:10:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接受时代吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.88,0:10:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后，变回仁慈的卡特尔好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.95,0:10:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藉这机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.12,0:10:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能令卡特尔你冷静下来就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.59,0:10:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藉这机会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.56,0:10:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.40,0:10:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛!放开我!特洛瓦会死!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.44,0:10:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，是你杀死他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.01,0:10:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.75,0:10:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,疯狂的家伙…我要把他杀死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.19,0:11:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么你就打倒我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.45,0:11:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后去救特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.32,0:11:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来你以那么\N天真的想法在战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.46,0:11:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白费了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.26,0:11:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦的死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.47,0:11:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔…我要…杀死你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.01,0:11:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.65,0:11:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.72,0:11:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要太过为难卡特尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.19,0:11:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.47,0:11:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙的科技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.27,0:11:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藉着我们罗姆斐拉财团的财力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.24,0:11:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开花结果的时候来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.21,0:11:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ终于完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.75,0:12:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD的量产准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.62,0:12:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身为支配阶级的我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.32,0:12:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把MD布署在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.02,0:12:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各国的纷争地域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.89,0:12:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藉着告诉全世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.06,0:12:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们拥有多强大的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.89,0:12:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赐予全世界秩序
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.90,0:12:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后再次迎接
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.73,0:12:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古老良好传统和礼法的时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.77,0:12:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,统一全世界吧!各位!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.08,0:12:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯，今后OZ也拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.78,0:12:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪尔麦优侯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.52,0:12:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我对罗姆斐拉财团要走的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.12,0:12:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不敢苟同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.72,0:12:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.42,0:12:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古老良好传统是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.43,0:12:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类的深奥感情构成的历史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.00,0:12:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我觉得战斗是美丽的同时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.80,0:12:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会申诉生命是平等的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.14,0:13:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会向逝去的灵魂表示哀悼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.91,0:13:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为人类须要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.54,0:13:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并非绝对的胜利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.51,0:13:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是战斗的姿态和理念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.18,0:13:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，罗姆斐拉财团使用MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.89,0:13:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种无心的战斗兵器\N建立的时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.46,0:13:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会成为被后世不耻的文化吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.19,0:13:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.46,0:13:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赞扬不能不战斗的人性的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.00,0:13:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.90,0:13:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我觉得宇宙卫星的思想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.70,0:13:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不知道那传统的无知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.90,0:13:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所产生的可怜牢骚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.87,0:13:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!死神!不要轻易被毁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.41,0:13:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你没事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.18,0:13:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二次演习开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.13,0:13:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶!可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.00,0:14:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.44,0:14:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的…眼泪吗…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.17,0:14:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，从那种恐惧中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.44,0:14:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,超越我的理想的新战士诞生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.21,0:14:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是钢弹的驾驶员们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.22,0:14:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父亲大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.56,0:14:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们怕死呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.79,0:14:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，不要战斗就行了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.13,0:14:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在他们充满纯真的感情前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.40,0:14:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传统会看不清楚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.41,0:14:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失去要保护的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.41,0:14:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兼且被保护的人出卖的战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.98,0:14:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在历史上是败者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.41,0:14:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，他们没有那种认识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.85,0:14:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们自己反而还充满战意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.56,0:14:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是为了有奇蹟发生的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.42,0:15:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在做现在能做的最佳事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.97,0:15:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果一切疯狂的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.57,0:15:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就会相信自己而战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.57,0:15:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人被认为美丽的\N感情总是悲哀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.14,0:15:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重视的传统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.65,0:15:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会在弱者们的叫喊中消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.95,0:15:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗里的胜者在历史中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.98,0:15:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要画上称为衰退的休止符
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.05,0:15:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有朝气的气息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.66,0:15:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会从败者之中培养出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.46,0:15:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯，你想说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.19,0:15:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想成为败者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.66,0:15:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，你是说罗姆斐拉财团总部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.47,0:15:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从你手上没收OZ比较好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.74,0:15:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们做不出血腥的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.95,0:15:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也因为你一直以来有功绩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.42,0:15:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要把你软禁\N在罗姆斐拉财团总部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.59,0:16:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使用扮成忘记战斗的枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.46,0:16:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,射穿敌人的胸膛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.80,0:16:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那也不会令我感动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.07,0:16:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋并非不正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.50,0:16:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们的心是自由的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.24,0:16:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,月面基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.44,0:16:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进入巴尔吉雷射炮\N的直接射程内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.78,0:16:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进攻方向发现月面基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.91,0:16:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布署的MD陶拉斯部队!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.08,0:16:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它们已经准备攻击!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.79,0:16:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,联络到月面基地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.15,0:16:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.82,0:16:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴尔吉的移动\N不在今日的程序里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.73,0:16:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD差一点就会开始攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.90,0:16:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毫不留情的兵器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.93,0:16:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是MD吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.67,0:16:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.47,0:16:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里的量产系统也完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.91,0:16:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是罗姆斐拉财团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.54,0:16:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为地球带来秩序的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.94,0:16:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最强士兵的完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.31,0:17:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看来明白特列斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.78,0:17:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讨厌MD的心情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.92,0:17:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.15,0:17:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯大人爱别人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.49,0:17:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且也爱人的死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.79,0:17:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死亡有强烈打动\N人类感情的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.29,0:17:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死亡给予的感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.30,0:17:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对战斗的肯定和否定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.10,0:17:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兴奋的感情会引致极端的选择
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.77,0:17:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接受死亡才是战士正确的模样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.08,0:17:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是弱者的想法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.55,0:17:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们现在诞生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.25,0:17:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,名为MD的不死战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.02,0:17:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们在建立\N超越死亡的战斗历史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.76,0:17:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兹巴洛夫，你没发觉吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.46,0:17:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD并非超越死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.46,0:17:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它们是你们害怕死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.13,0:17:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,担任替身的人偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.97,0:17:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们不可能参加\N预料会输的战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.01,0:18:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胜败没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.57,0:18:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不断战斗会令感情经历锻炼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.78,0:18:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逝去的灵魂得到回报的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.28,0:18:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,终有一日也会来临吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.18,0:18:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是我不能理解的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.12,0:18:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以你和我才成为敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.56,0:18:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,指示MD进行对要塞战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.27,0:18:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们会用巴尔吉雷射炮攻击基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.74,0:18:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他想不到巴尔吉是饵吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.21,0:18:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果用巴尔吉雷射炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.44,0:18:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不能预测月面基地的损毁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.45,0:18:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别被攻陷啊，巴尔吉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.05,0:18:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会须要太久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.69,0:18:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十部里欧突破防卫线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.79,0:18:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阻止巴尔吉而疏于防守的闸口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.83,0:18:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被集中攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.53,0:18:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD在这里的布署
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.46,0:18:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全被知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.83,0:19:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才会有趣起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.74,0:19:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,占据MD\N生产工场，拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.17,0:19:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校你去哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.48,0:19:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去释放钢弹的驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.48,0:19:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯大人也希望那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.32,0:19:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人没有追击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.73,0:19:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，死守这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.49,0:19:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,队…队长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.86,0:19:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.90,0:19:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新型机已经能动了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.61,0:19:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能赶得上就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.85,0:19:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赶得及也好，我只须再处死他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.85,0:19:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，到时我也劳烦你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.65,0:19:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在OZ的错误
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.12,0:20:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是染血的过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.63,0:20:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来，开枪!兹巴洛夫
